 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"我地要對美國有信心，我地要對香港人有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"聽日我就點都出<br />\n但今次失敗左我真係唔覺得再有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1111fe17b3d270d05e77d2e4c542530d7c7884b8","tid":1549652,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"聽日兩點美國領事館呀，早d食完晏晝，咪次次都遲哂大到呀"},{"pid":"9f11c311072e26d1fcf87db987cf4c218b2c5ccb","tid":1549652,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:49:50.000Z","msg":"聽日唔出，人權法唔過，你以後都唔駛出街啦"},{"pid":"387f91ca63388431cd0d79618f40441c8290bcf7","tid":1549652,"uid":32022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"出啊 一定要出啊"},{"pid":"9401c63752542ff93db5263e19dc99c69a3f33ea","tid":1549652,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［拋磚］一人N個聽日用嘅英文口號<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549609</a>"},{"pid":"6cc77b1c050280c57b26a7a5c6d4b6eae03f1134","tid":1549652,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"想印國旗的手足注意<br />\n唔好行完就掉 要拎番旗番屋企<br />\n聽日 美領見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0ZYr1A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0ZYr1A.jpg&h=13bd6197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GA461A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GA461A.jpg&h=addfcf18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v48qRtf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv48qRtf.jpg&h=ab706bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"005ce04c71f26f1fa6011a91ef29a33d14779955","tid":1549652,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q74mpTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq74mpTy.jpg&h=be53c481&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cc679df883590742c4b46f49c32e16fbb9c1721","tid":1549652,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"想唱歌既聽朝練好先出街呀，有埋歌詞架<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=we6o7jzcTSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dwe6o7jzcTSI&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=617d57cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=we6o7jzcTSI</a>"},{"pid":"cb8cc72aef303ab184522ec402a19975778d1914","tid":1549652,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"12624c0ccd062acfed6e6e12034c8ac4c88c27e3","tid":1549652,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8cc72aef303ab184522ec402a19975778d1914","tid":1549652,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,